show.description: When warehouse worker Meera Sachdev crosses paths with billionaire heir Krish Malhotra, a night of fate binds them together forever. Torn between love and money, they must fight past secrets, family betrayals, and society’s judgment to protect their unborn child and discover what truly matters.
